</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="ED0ED57C4CA508DBA4C4922C6575621E" pageId="null" pageNumber="310" type="description">
<paragraph id="C126981F923FBA7F42CF9707D5BB7FE5" pageId="null" pageNumber="310">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="5FD7B77AF687328649A8F012E6EC9570" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rubiaceae" genus="Rubia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Gentianales" pageId="null" pageNumber="310" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="tinctorum">
<emphasis id="E6E7835644BDC43C784A5C0B0FC96C7B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="310">R. tinctorum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 1) durch folgende Merkmale: Stengel im untern Teil 
<emphasis id="119CC3EDA72F91ADAEA8667A5EA50EC3" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="310">
<normalizedToken id="C1593FE6EA07ABCE2261EE676826525F" originalValue="immergrün" pageId="null" pageNumber="310">immergruen</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
, 
<normalizedToken id="C38D6BA6C38F2B17C99CF3A3497C3B7B" originalValue="±" pageId="null" pageNumber="310">+/-</normalizedToken>
verholzt, oft lang kletternd; 
<emphasis id="66516808EA473880F9F4D0F3542E7882" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="310">
<normalizedToken id="706058F196A04B1130E0CF89E2DC0E0F" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="310">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
ungestielt
</emphasis>
, unterseits keine Netznerven sichtbar, oft zu 6 oder mehr im Quirl; 
<emphasis id="3C60064C4B47727A99FD4EA8A782E039" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="310">Krone im Durchmesser 3</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="0A95AC64643A635D2F2890567D2626FE" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="310">6 mm; Staubbeutel</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="1777DAB3FA311E4C3D579A7F67FD03F4" originalValue="±" pageId="null" pageNumber="310">+/-</normalizedToken>
<emphasis id="A8C342891CFB7699B08581EFF8685F81" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="310">kugelig, 0,2</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="0E07613244E4727CC842E2F3B66CEC32" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="310">0,3 mm lang; Griffel nur im obern Teil 2teilig;</emphasis>
Frucht 3-4 mm hoch. - 
<normalizedToken id="84C2037520477A33BD9F41A89464AF09" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="310">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken id="0B8ABA968FDA901A72978A25A929B3C2" originalValue="Später" pageId="null" pageNumber="310">Spaeter</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="72DD7D3CB95957E07A26EF1E9AEFA47E" originalValue="Frühling" pageId="null" pageNumber="310">Fruehling</normalizedToken>
und 
<normalizedToken id="658CD8D095A4875AA7B0F3A93581D441" originalValue="früher" pageId="null" pageNumber="310">frueher</normalizedToken>
Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="B5EA4A50446A7794DB7083339FAAEC3F" pageId="null" pageNumber="310">
<emphasis id="F8208F9DBCFBF12BF10298F084F2D3DF" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="310">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="555F04BB28E7FB008C521E2C52009BEB" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="310">44:</emphasis>
Material von den Balearen (Nilsson und Lassen 1971, Dahlgren et al. 1971). 
<emphasis id="8ECB6A9A526566DB00725560533A2D66" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="310">2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="5A54C74815C61393B32D5DF51E873CE9" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="310">66:</emphasis>
Material aus Frankreich (Poucques 1949). 
<emphasis id="9EE269BBB26860B92F561B04323F8B8C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="310">2n ca. 132:</emphasis>
Material ohne Herkunftsangabe (Fagerlind 1937).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="987F7D842CDF1BFF8F260D8C1CAFCEBA" pageId="null" pageNumber="310">
<emphasis id="9863051FB15944BB072B80EBD0C5B07C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="310">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin. Trockene 
<normalizedToken id="E81F83AD0A695E46219CBE8C05C03A08" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="310">Boeden</normalizedToken>
in warmen, halbschattigen Lagen. 
<normalizedToken id="52341952CDBFAE2BA909DC22A0FBA2B1" originalValue="Immergrüne" pageId="null" pageNumber="310">Immergruene</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="F5DF5781D581AF4458CF1DDA3234ED7F" originalValue="Eichenwälder" pageId="null" pageNumber="310">Eichenwaelder</normalizedToken>
, Macchien.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="56E69CECFA40375728BBD4597BDDF80B" pageId="null" pageNumber="310">
<emphasis id="0DAC5AEEC6C648C270BA147DDA629D66" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="310">
Verbreitung. 
<normalizedToken id="16DF40940C2E4E443099A5271E69582B" originalValue="Westeuropäisch-mediterrane" pageId="null" pageNumber="310">Westeuropaeisch-mediterrane</normalizedToken>
Pflanze:
</emphasis>
Ganzes Mittelmeergebiet; 
<normalizedToken id="857AE9ACD20E8B0A7F1E0593177D5EFF" originalValue="nordwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="310">nordwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Irland, England, Gegend der untern Seine, 
<normalizedToken id="44FF5A6E1BA0DD66830C7CF79DA78F19" originalValue="südliche" pageId="null" pageNumber="310">suedliche</normalizedToken>
Alpen, Balkanhalbinsel. - Im Gebiet: 
<normalizedToken id="AD0942B8602B8F025FCABA7261E498A8" originalValue="Südliches" pageId="null" pageNumber="310">Suedliches</normalizedToken>
Savoyen (im Jura 
<normalizedToken id="E2B9BDE46224D15A2ECFAA912E84C920" originalValue="nordwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="310">nordwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Val de Fier; im 
<normalizedToken id="678D06B145C3B1CC760BCDE089CE7FC3" originalValue="Isèretal" pageId="null" pageNumber="310">Iseretal</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="C09D60D66501C4A78ADB8A52DE88D0FE" originalValue="aufwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="310">aufwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis in die untere Maurienne; Gegend des Lac de Bourget, Lac 
<normalizedToken id="D45C4C1E644082E2F85BA780673F1D60" originalValue="d’Annecy" pageId="null" pageNumber="310">d'Annecy</normalizedToken>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
